《'''完美謊情'''》（{{lang-it|'''Perfetti sconosciuti'''}}）是2016年由義大利導演{{link-it|保羅·傑諾維西|Paolo Genovese}}執導的電影作品，本片獲得[[義大利電影金像獎|義大利電影金像獎]]最佳影片，並在義大利上映時票房超過1600萬歐元。<ref name="Anderson">{{cite web|url= http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/italy-box-office-local-comedy-866302|title= Italy Box Office: Local Comedy Trumps 'Zoolander 2' Debut|first= Ariston|last= Anderson|date= February 16, 2016|accessdate= February 19, 2016|work= The Hollywood Reporter|archive-date= 2016-11-27|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161127094049/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/italy-box-office-local-comedy-866302|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name="cinematographe">{{cite web|url= http://www.cinematographe.it/46882/news/perfetti-sconosciuti-data-uscita.html|title= Perfetti Sconosciuti: il film di Paolo Genovese al cinema dall’11 Febbraio|date= December 24, 2015|accessdate= February 19, 2016|work= cinematographe.it|language= it|archive-date= 2016-03-12|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160312125942/http://www.cinematographe.it/46882/news/perfetti-sconosciuti-data-uscita.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>

== 劇情 ==
三對夫妻（羅科和伊娃、萊勒和卡洛塔、科西莫和比安卡）及一男子佩普藉著[[月蝕|月蝕]]之夜，舉辦賞月蝕活動兼老友聚會，期間伊娃向出席聚會的一行人提議玩公開手機的遊戲，無論收到簡訊、接到電話都必須公開，最後卻演變成人人互相猜疑，終至關係失控。

